{"h059543a8g397bg4102gb7e7g75985c8e720a": ["*Sniff.*", "3b92c689-6024-4446-a6c9-584e9e8d77ca", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_AfterHarpyEncounter.html", "2e3a7dcd-1c8c-b5a1-1e8f-e8fc5e43b42e"], "h19c22ae3g949ag43f1g94fcg8d3ab71e2b77": ["A-are they gone?", "3b92c689-6024-4446-a6c9-584e9e8d77ca", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_AfterHarpyEncounter.html", "94ba2620-4b5c-3e8d-f112-e55c5119df18"], "h11ec1650ge72dg468cgbe8bg0727c887db9a": ["They're gone. Are you all right?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_AfterHarpyEncounter.html", "d06d0afe-429b-ce85-0773-bc4f227905b8"], "h8446519dg4137g49e1g8ddfg186866f52517": ["<i>Sing a soothing lullaby.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_AfterHarpyEncounter.html", "98ce2cf9-b4a7-bf34-7285-6ef86fe1cfdc"], "h26710410geea1g48f5ga282gd64fda5585e8": ["W-who are you?", "3b92c689-6024-4446-a6c9-584e9e8d77ca", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_AfterHarpyEncounter.html", "0105860e-2456-4932-fe92-e56a3acdcaa8"], "h8ed4a52cg832cg45beg8f2egdd1bfc3032a4": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_AfterHarpyEncounter.html", "c8ba548d-9769-6e02-d675-e63d0ee829dc"], "ha4107570g344cg4118gb98cg40cd7f5fd884": ["Wauw... I'm Mirkon, I - oh no.", "3b92c689-6024-4446-a6c9-584e9e8d77ca", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_AfterHarpyEncounter.html", "6d8cf6be-32c6-5eba-4484-5cc5d057d0f4"], "hd0b05787g6617g4ef4g9ab2gb62d9a98e6cf": ["I-I had to get the gold from the nest. Mol will be so mad. I got to go.", "3b92c689-6024-4446-a6c9-584e9e8d77ca", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_AfterHarpyEncounter.html", "4e5dfa8a-cd88-57a6-c216-098c7a059fd4"], "h82b8f21bgeedfg40fdg84d9g38872da4d6d3": ["Never mind that - are you all right?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_AfterHarpyEncounter.html", "9a2caaa8-edc2-d7ea-7c59-c7fba658a041"], "hfd914f3fg42f3g4929gbce4g399c4f